a conversation privately

137
00:06:00,447 --> 00:06:01,997
in the conference room.

138
00:06:02,031 --> 00:06:03,665
Don't eat the cupcake.

139
00:06:05,804 --> 00:06:08,768
We are here today

140
00:06:08,857 --> 00:06:13,160
