planting here is dead bodies.

148
00:06:29,344 --> 00:06:31,495
That's fine,
'cause they're not gonna grow.

149
00:06:31,529 --> 00:06:33,297
Well, thank God they're not,

150
00:06:33,331 --> 00:06:34,731
