thoughts that are in my head.

228
00:09:53,181 --> 00:09:55,132
Hmm.
[Forced chuckle]

229
00:09:55,166 --> 00:09:56,566
Hey!

230
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:59,236
I have a crazy feeling...

231
